<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb the alliance. As with <i>Eleocharis palustris, E. acicularis </i>is top-killed by fire when actively growing, yet it survives as rhizomes and establishes from seed after fires (Hauser 2006c).</div>
